Text: Huh?! This is to wear?

Yes, these are the clothes that Lady Gamma picked
out.
These are...clothes? They're all sparkly and bulky.
Totally different from the clothes I know!

Lady Gamma said this is the formal dress for the
Therianthrope Shrine...

Now that you mention it, I think that some people at
the shrine were wearing things like this...

I've never worn this kinda thing. No! I don't wanna
wear it!

I understand that you don't want to wear unfamiliar
clothes, but you've been ordered to...
Why should I follow orders from Gamma?!

An order from Boss man or Alpha is different, but
Gamma is weaker than me!
No, this is an order from Lady Alpha.
Urk!

I will say it again. This is an order from Lady
Alpha. Ahem.

Okay, Delta? You are to be a guide. This time, the
Shadow Garden...

Rather, we are going as Shadow's representatives, and
when in Oriana, do as the Orianans do.
Repre..sent?
...Wearing these clothes is a rule of the shrine.
I see!
I'm glad you understand. So now―
I hate it.
What? You just said―

I didn't say I would wear it! I don't like how I
can't move easily in it! I don't like it!

But you have to wear it. Otherwise, I will get told
off.
I don't know nothin 'bout Nu getting told off!
Delta, you will get told off too…
Urk, th-that's... Anyway, not wearing it!
This is a problem...

Really, Delta. We are busy with measurements here.
What are you stamping your feet about?

I don't wanna wear weird clothes! I'll wear my slime
suit!

If we could all do that, life would be much easier...
These are complicated clothes, so it's difficult
to maintain their shape.
Grr, you're trying to confuse me with all the big words!
*sigh*... if you hate it so much, then don't be a guide.

Tell me the location. I will wear a kimono and go
with Lady Alpha myself.
Huh? No way! I want to go!

Then stop being selfish and put the clothes on. Is it
really that bad if I go in your place?
Just try going, Gamma! I bet you'll fall!
Hmm...it is hard to deny that…

Anyway, look! To start, just try putting your arms
through the sleeves! You might find it is quite
comfortable!
It's a flappy thing. I know it will be hard to move in.

The fabric is certainly a little heavy... But try
touching it. See, it's very smooth.
Smooth?
Delta takes a fingertip to the cloth.
You're right, it's smooth...

Right? It's comfortable, isn't it? It's quite airy,
and you don't get sweaty...
How long will this Mitsugoshi sales talk take?
Oh, Lady Alpha!
So, Delta, what do you think of the kimono?
It's sparkly... And much cooler than I thought!
Exactly. You want to be sparkly and cool right?
Yeah, and more than that, it's easy to move in...
You can get used to it, right?
Ha-ruff... I can...get used to it...

(I got scared cuz Lady Alpha was smiling, but her
eyes weren't smiling...)

Great, try it on. I am sure it will be more
comfortable than you think.
Ahh... My tummy hurts so much...!

You can put up with your waist being slimmer. It's
something that women have to put up with.
Slimmer... Slammer... Gamma...
Don't say stupid things!
Grrrrr!

*huff, huff* People really wear this? It's harder to
move in than I thought…

Yes, it certainly does seem a little tight. Looks
like you are putting up with it. And building up
stress...

At this rate, you're going to explode before you can
guide me to the shrine. This is a disaster waiting to
happen.
Waaaah... I can't take this Gamma Slamma Slimmer stuff any more...

That's why you don't mess around with people's
names...
What's the big fuss? Are we all dressed?

Cid...! Actually, we are having difficulties getting
Delta dressed...

(Lady Alpha glanced in my direction. At this rate,
Boss man is gonna get angry...)

Delta says it's hard to move in and is refusing to
keep it on... I guess it does seem tight.
I see. How about holding back the sleeves?
Hold back the sleeves...?
Could this be Shadow Wisdom?!

I wouldn't really call it wisdom. Let me have a
look.
Delta, can you hold on, just a little?
Y-Yeah. Okay…
So this is with the sleeves held back...!

Yup. I think this way your arms will be freer.
How is it?

Ohh, I didn't know sleeves can be loose like this. I
can move!

Yup yup. The kimono sash is probably a little tight,
but you should get used to it.
Yeah, it seems so...!

It was sooo tight at first, but now it fits my tummy
perfectly!

It's like I'm wearing a slime suit! Wow! Thanks, Boss
man!

Boss man knows so much and can quickly do anything!
That's why you're Boss man!

You were a big help. Finally, we can go get some
New Year's rice cakes.
Oh, rice cakes...

(Honestly, it is a different world, so I can't expect
too much. But no need for me to say that out loud...)

Yeah, looking forward to them. Go enjoy your New Year
visit to the shrine.
We will! Come on, Delta. Let's go.
Okay! We'll be back!
Okay, let's go home!
(I went with Lady Alpha to the Therianthrope Shrine!)

(I wonder what interesting things are ahead... I am
so excited!)
